<section id="Hypervisor_Network_Screen" remap="TID_7857">
	<title>Node Network Screen</title>
	<para>
		The <guilabel>Network</guilabel> screen is used to configure:
	</para>
	<itemizedlist>
		<listitem>
			<para>
				the Node's hostname,
			</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>
				the <acronym> DNS</acronym> server(s) to use,
			</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>
				the <acronym> NTP</acronym> server(s) to use, and
			</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>
				the network interface to use.
			</para>
		</listitem>
	</itemizedlist>
